{"tid":1996434,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃國桐律師計劃在台北開二手衣物店","createTime":"2020-05-01T03:23:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T10:03:40.000Z","uid":23707,"like":160,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"b9c31371b5e7da997ac0678bd1631fc427f183eb","tid":1996434,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T03:23:30.000Z","msg":"#街坊報料 繼「保護傘」餐廳終於在台北營業，黃國桐律師下一個計劃&mdash;&mdash;在台北開二手衣物店，終於開始籌備了。 拜託有心人將有出售價值的衣服（不需要鞋）先清潔好，然後分類，分男裝、女裝及童裝，請送去下列地址🙏🙏 九龍城福佬村道49號A閣樓 黃國桐區議員 去之前請通知： 黃國桐區議員的助理區先生（2336 0089/ wongkwoktung2019@dphk.org） #撐手足 #齊上齊落<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n醬油：<a href=\"https://www.babydiscuss.com/t/topic/16522\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.babydiscuss.com%2Ft%2Ftopic%2F16522&d=IJrjZyikD9iZithZGIL3rD2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=5e8d5933\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.babydiscuss.com/t/topic/16522</a>"},{"pid":"959deda32a2f1e8580b7b06318fb20d07490deee","tid":1996434,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T03:25:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36deadf08588a6878c44a1745d63ee9da6ff261d","tid":1996434,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T03:28:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed837a684e4d3e196c5e21aaa15f6570bb2940af","tid":1996434,"uid":8014,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T03:32:11.000Z","msg":"有得做 香港人大撚把衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n貪平買完之後著1~2次就封塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4e05aea2daed168cb519a74300550e6bc2064ae","tid":1996434,"uid":103916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor